Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.33,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k534}Do you know there's an animal that can theoretically live forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.54,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k220}Wait, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.33,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k280}That sounds like something out of a fantasy novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:11.43,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k109}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:18.53,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k710}It's not a mythical beast at all, but a tiny jellyfish known as the Immortal Jellyfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:22.78,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k424}Its scientific name is Turatopsis Dorny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.37,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k259}An immortal jellyfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.37,0:00:27.01,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k164}That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.92,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k190}Where are these things found?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.50,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k357}They're found in oceans all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:37.06,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k456}And what makes them immortal is their remarkable survival skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.38,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k232}What kind of skill are we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.38,0:00:45.64,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k625}When faced with old age, injury, or even starvation, it doesn't just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:53.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k820}It can reverse its entire life cycle, transforming back into its earliest stage, a polyp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:57.24,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k339}So it just becomes a baby again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.11,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k187}That's wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:02.10,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k298}Does it then grow into a new jellyfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:03.60,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k150}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k624}From that polyp, a new, genetically identical jellyfish will eventually grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:15.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k600}Imagine a butterfly being able to turn back into a caterpillar and start its life all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:16.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k100}over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:17.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k100}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:21.35,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k351}That's such a perfect analogy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.92,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k356}So scientists must be really interested in this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:26.40,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k148}Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:32.15,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k575}This unique ability to essentially cheat death has fascinated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:36.68,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k452}They're studying it closely to unlock secrets about aging.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.84,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k115}That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:43.28,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k543}A tiny creature deep in the ocean holding a potential key to immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:46.31,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k303}That's a pretty big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:46.95,Highlight,,0,0,0,,{\k64}Now I know.
